    <name>Wine route: Venthône – Leuk (Stage 4)</name>
    <desc>The final stage of the wine route connects the French-speaking with the German-speaking Valais and leads through medieval villages, the extensive Pfyn-Finges Nature Park, and to an innovative wine center.</desc>
